### Agent procedure reference

Procedure **bodies** live under [`.reinguard/procedure/`](../../.reinguard/procedure/) (SSOT). **Cursor entries:** [`rgd-next.md`](../commands/rgd-next.md) — `rgd context build`, Route, **Propose** (once), then **Execute** with `next-orchestration.md`; [`cursor-plan.md`](../commands/cursor-plan.md) — `AskQuestion` / `CreatePlan` only (`gh issue create` appears as plan todos when issue-first). **After `cursor-plan` acceptance, execution must use `rgd-next` loop semantics** (`next-orchestration.md` § Loop semantics) — `cursor-plan` does not define execution; it produces the plan that `rgd-next` Execute consumes.

Use `gh` CLI for observation (`gh issue view`, `gh pr view`, `gh pr checks`, etc.) until full `rgd observe` coverage.

